text: Luterbach-Attisholz railway station () is a railway station in the municipality of Luterbach, in the Swiss canton of Solothurn. It is an intermediate stop on the standard gauge Jura Foot line and is served by local trains only. == Services == The following services stop at Luterbach- Attisholz: * Regio: ** half-hourly service between and , with every other train continuing from Solothurn to . ** hourly service between and Olten; limited service continuing from Langendorf to and . == References == == External links == * * Category:Railway stations in the canton of Solothurn Category:Swiss Federal Railways stations
